 <br /> Malawi is the land of rolling hills along with its Great lake Malawi, which runs almost the entire length of the country, the scenery is endlessly spectacular, a true photographers dream.<br /> <br /> Volunteer In Africa has some of the most inspirational placements in Malawi, whether it be in the city of Blantyre, or in some of the villages near Mangochi on lake Malawi, everyone leaves Malawi truly inspired ready for more of lifes adventures. <br /> <br /> When you choose Volunteer In Africa your stay is extremely important to us, although we are not a tour company we are very interested to make sure your experience is complete.<br /> <br /> If you wish to experience village life, Lake Malawi, or some of this countries beautiful culture and heritage, whether it be on your weekend breaks from volunteering or on a trip after your time with us, we are happy to stear you in the right direction. <br /> <br /> The program intakes happen twice per month - on the first and the third weekend.\",\"alignment\":\"\",\"text_fontsize\":\"\",\"text_lineheight\":\"\",\"text_fontweight\":\"\",\"dropcap\":0,\"class\":\"\",\"global_background_type\":\"none\",\"global_background_gradient\":{\"color\":\"#00c6fb\",\"color2\":\"#005bea\",\"deg\":\"45\",\"type\":\"linear\"},\"global_background_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"global_background_size\":\"cover\",\"global_background_attachment\":\"inherit\",\"global_background_position\":\"50% 50%\",\"global_use_overlay\":0,\"global_overlay_type\":\"overlay_none\",\"global_gradient_overlay\":{\"color\":\"rgba(127, 0, 255, 0.8)\",\"color2\":\"rgba(225, 0, 255, 0.7)\",\"deg\":\"45\",\"type\":\"linear\"},\"global_pattern_overlay\":\"\",\"global_overlay_pattern_color\":\"\",\"blend_mode\":\"normal\",\"global_user_border\":0,\"global_border_width\":\"\",\"global_border_radius\":0,\"global_margin\":{\"md\":\"0px 0px 30px 0px\",\"sm\":\"0px 0px 20px 0px\",\"xs\":\"0px 0px 10px 0px\"},\"global_padding\":\"\",\"global_boxshadow\":\"0 0 0 0 #ffffff\",